The PS8640 DSI-to-eDP bridge can retrieve the EDID, so implement the
.get_edid callback and set the flag to indicate the core to use it.

Signed-off-by: Enric Balletbo i Serra <enric.balletbo@collabora.com>
---

Changes in v2: None

